{"_path":"/maps/_ai/tools/copilot","_dir":"tools","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"Copilot","description":"Copilot 是一种新型人机协作工具。","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"domain"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Domain"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_ai/prompt/team-based-instructions"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Team based Instructions"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_ai/prompt/context-engineering"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Context Engineering"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"cross-domain"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Cross Domain"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_programming/dx/genai-for-legacy-codebases"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GenAI for Legacy Codebases"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"gists"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Gists"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"团队-ai-编码率稳步提升到-892-的-ai-coding-实践分享"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/dq87Orqr8SyeyECZg3BMfA","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"团队 AI 编码率稳步提升到 89.2% 的 AI Coding 实践分享"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"饿了么团队把 AI 编码采纳率从 9.6% 提到 89.2%，需求交付效率提升 23.6%。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"q","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"幻觉是AI的天性，不可避免，只能尽量减少。而我们要的是AI给我们生成确定性的、高质量的内容。这就需要从两方面入手，一方面需要保障我们输入给AI的内容质量；另一方面我们需要提出规范及要求让AI按照我们的预期生成内容，保障AI输出给我们的质量。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"统一上下文"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"三层架构模板：数据-逻辑-应用层固定目录结构，先让 AI 生成“地图”再写代码。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"技术方案模版：把需求拆成“领域功能+应用服务+业务规则+数据模型”四格表，人工只填业务，其余交给 AI。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"结构化 Prompt"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"分层提示：按“架构层-模块-类-函数”四级写要求，不含任何业务词，保证跨需求复用。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"增量调优：每周收一次 bad case，把新规则写进 Prompt，版本号随 CI 自动升级。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"任务粒度控制"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"类级单元：一次请求只生成一个完整类，过大再拆接口-实现两份。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"先方案后代码：PRD→AI 生成技术方案→人工 Review→AI 按方案写代码，防止幻觉跑偏。"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"阶段总结，形成了一套高质量的体系化的AI+Prompt+技术方案模版+工程结构的AI编码方案。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/20251204113817450.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"接口类提示词设计："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/20251204114413996.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/20251204114154426.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"child